# Detailed Feature & Architecture Plan: Azure + Supabase RAG + Tier Enforcement

This document outlines the architectural split for CloudCode's AI roadmap. To optimize costs and keep your monthly running bills at **$0 (fixed)**, we are routing all generative intelligence to **Azure OpenAI / Azure AI Foundry** (which consumes your $100 credits) while building the search indexer (RAG) directly on your **Supabase DB** via `pgvector`.

Additionally, we are **activating token logging and tier enforcement** to ensure that your free Azure credits are protected from abuse by free-tier users.

